~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : read                                      ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : read [<roomname>/<boardname>]

   This displays the message board of a given room or free board.  
   If no argument is supplied it assumes your current room as befault.
   you can only read the room you are currently in unless you are a wiz.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : write, search, wipe
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
